cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with searching large video corpora using natural language queries, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) and multimedia (MM) aspects, which makes cs.IR and cs.MM likely sub-categories as well. Finally, the paper uses compositional semantics to encode subtle meaning, which falls under the category of machine learning (LG), making cs.LG a possible sub-category.
